@HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

# OpenAI-Compatible Chat Completions API

### Simple Chat - First Message
POST {{HostAddress}}/TravelAssistant/v1/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "gpt-4o",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "What are some must-visit places in Australia?"
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Australia has many incredible destinations! Here are some must-visit places:\n\n1. **Sydney** - Famous for the Opera House and Harbour Bridge\n2. **Great Barrier Reef** - World's largest coral reef system, perfect for snorkeling and diving\n3. **Melbourne** - Known for its arts, culture, and coffee scene\n4. **Uluru (Ayers Rock)** - Iconic red rock formation in the heart of Australia\n5. **Gold Coast** - Beautiful beaches and theme parks\n6. **Tasmania** - Stunning wilderness and wildlife\n7. **Cairns** - Gateway to the Great Barrier Reef and rainforests\n\nEach destination offers unique experiences. What type of activities are you most interested in?"
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Which one would you recommend for families with kids?"
    }
  ]
}

# OpenAI-Compatible Responses API

### Create a Conversation
POST {{HostAddress}}/v1/conversations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
  ]
}

### Response API
# First create a conversation using the endpoint above, then use the conversation ID here
POST {{HostAddress}}/TravelAssistant/v1/responses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "stream": false,
  "conversation": "conv_YOUR_CONVERSATION_ID_HERE",
  "input": [
    {
      "type": "message",
      "role": "user",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "input_text",
          "text": "What are some must-visit places in Australia?"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

### Get Conversation Items
# Replace with your conversation ID from the create conversation response
GET {{HostAddress}}/v1/conversations/conv_YOUR_CONVERSATION_ID_HERE/items?include=string
